PSI Net can probably no longer afford to go it alone, despite being
the nation's largest independent provide of Internet backbone
services. But until the time comes to merge or be acquired, this
renegade chief executive and his march-to-its-own-drummer company
mean to keep doing things their way _ and making sure that any
eventual deal will come at a high price to the other party. By Seth
Schiesel.
