<HEADLINE>
SEEING VICTORY IN THE JAWS OF RETREAT 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating)  (The Week in Review)  
(bl) 
 By SUSAN SACHS   
 c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
