<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-13 08:53 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5098 &Cx1f; var-z
u a BC-POLITICAL-INSULTS-TEX     03-13 1151
