<P>
   COLONCANCER-WEB _ Colon cancer is in the news in a big way: A
campaign headed by TV host Katie Couric, whose 42-year-old husband
died of the disease, is running on TV and in newspapers and
magazines, and has already succeeded in having March named National
Colon Cancer Awareness Month. Responding to the probable interest
on the part of readers - who may not know it is the second-most
lethal cancer - this is an expanded mediawatch with 5-6 sites.
(McKenna, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 17.
