<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-13 12:55 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5296 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r t BBC-LADN-TRAVEL-CALIFORN     03-13 0072
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-LADN-TRAVEL-CALIFORNIA </SLUG>
 B DESSERT-ANZA BORREGO-LADN  
<TEXT>
<P>
   The Los Angeles Daily News plans to move the following feature
stories for use by NYTimes News Service clients for Monday, March
13 and thereafter. For questions about stories, please contact
Marge Powers at the Daily News, (818) 713-3691.
</P>
<P>
   ANZA BORREGO _ Dessert Jewel. Little-known Anza Borrego is a
place to get away from it all.
</P>
<P>
   With art
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
<TRAILER>
NYT-03-13-00 1255EST &QL; 
</TRAILER>
