<SLUG> BC-DINOSAURS-AZR </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
DINOSAURS' EVOLUTION CONTINUES EVEN TODAY 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
 By RICHARD NILSEN  
 c.2000 The Arizona Republic  
 (EDITORS: ALSO MOVED IN THE ``E'' CATEGORY) 
