<SLUG> BC-TRIBUNE-IMPACT-ART-NYT </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
MERGER ANNOUNCEMENT IS BAD NEWS FOR TRIBUNE SHAREHOLDERS 
</HEADLINE>
 (With TRIBUNE-TIMESMEDIA) 
(ART ADV: Graphic is being sent to NYT graphic clients.
Nonsubscribers can make individual purchase by calling 888-603-1036
or 888-346-9867.) 
(nk) 
 By ALEX BERENSON   
 c.2000 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   The Tribune Co.'s agreement to buy Times Mirror spelled bad news
for Tribune shareholders on Monday.
</P>
