Tournament notebook. 
By Jon Wilner. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
BKC-PEPPERDINE-NOTEBOOK (Malibu, Calif.) _ A Pepperdine men's
basketball NCAA Tournament notebook. 
By Vincent Bonsignore. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 
 
 
BKC-PEPPERDINE-OPPONENT (Malibu, Calif.) _ A profile of Indiana
University, Pepperdine's first-round opponent in the NCAA
Tournament. 
By Vincent Bonsignore. (Will move on the ``s'' sports file.) 
 
 

<TEXT>
<P>
</P>
</TEXT>
